[[Image:BPSA Logo Only Outline.jpg|thumb|right|200px|Logo of the Bio Process Systems Alliance.]] The '''Bio Process Systems Alliance''' (BPSA) is a [[biopharmaceutical]] [[industry trade group]] of suppliers of [[single use components]] and [[single use systems]] for manufacturing processes. It was created in 2006 through an alliance of 26 suppliers.
